# Performance Requirements

Crash detection latency <5 ms

Watchdog overhead <1% CPU

Logging throughput >100,000 messages/sec

Recovery time <2 seconds

Memory overhead <20 MB

Thread-safe

Lock-free where appropriate

Zero memory leaks

