# Deliverables

Provide:

* Production-quality source code
* Modular architecture
* CMake build system
* Comprehensive documentation
* Unit and integration tests
* Sample configurations
* Example applications
* Benchmark results
* Logging and metrics examples
* CI/CD pipeline configuration (GitHub Actions)
* Docker support
* Static analysis configuration
* Code formatting configuration
* Automated testing scripts

The generated code should follow modern C++20 best practices, use RAII, smart pointers, constexpr where appropriate, strong type safety, modular design, minimal external dependencies, clear separation of concerns, and be written with maintainability, scalability, and fault tolerance as primary goals.
